included North America 24 per cent, UK exports 41 per cent, and power tools
66 per cent.
Operating profit came to Pounds 801,000 (Pounds 1.79m) and the pre-tax
balance to Pounds 809,000 (Pounds 1.57m). Earnings per share fell to 1.22p
(3.32p) and the interim dividend is again 1.15p on higher capital.
