<TEXT>
Sir, Last week the Engineering Council told us that it wanted to add
technology to the list of A-levels ('Engineers warn on A-level courses',
September 1). This week, the British Institute of Management tells us that
it wants to replace all A-levels ('Patten steps up GCSE attack', September
