Leif Mills. CPSA: Mr Barry Reamsbottom. NASUWT: Mr Nigel de Gruchy. NCU: Mr
Tony Young. NUCPS: Mr Leslie Christie. RMT: Mr Jimmy Knapp. NUT: Mr Doug
McAvoy. UCW: Mr Alan Tuffin.
Section C (elected from unions with less than 100,000 members). IPMS: Mr
